Package org.jivesoftware.openfire.roster

Interface Summary
RosterEventListener Interface to listen for roster events.
 

Class Summary
Roster A roster is a list of users that the user wishes to know if they are online.
RosterEventDispatcher Dispatches roster events.
RosterItem Represents a single roster item for a User's Roster.
RosterItem.AskType  
RosterItem.RecvType  
RosterItem.SubType  
RosterItemProvider Defines the provider methods required for creating, reading, updating and deleting roster items.
RosterManager A simple service that allows components to retrieve a roster based solely on the ID of the owner.
